openSSCF
an open-source c++ code of Socket-based Server/client Framework.

Server: openSSCF_s_linux
				linked and debuged by gcc~
				take a closer look at the makeFile
Client: openSSCF_c_win
				linked and debuged by VS11
				uncomment and try each client's operation in the main()
				
